OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBBC announces changes to   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcomplaints process         
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The BBC has announced changes to its   
OL,6, complaints process, vowing to make it  
OL,7, easier and more transparent.           
OL,9,FThe corporation said that in order to  
OL,10,F"maintain audience trust" it would make
OL,11,Fits complaints website easier to find  
OL,12,Fand use.                               
OL,14,FIt follows a review by media watchdog  
OL,15,FOfcom, which said the BBC needed to be 
OL,16,Fmore "open and clear with audiences".  
OL,18,FThe changes, expected within six       
OL,19,Fmonths, will aim to help improve how   
OL,20,Feditorial teams respond to complaints. 
